00:45:33.190 --> 00:45:38.010
of its-- well for one, in
many self-defense scenarios

00:45:38.010 --> 00:45:40.721
that women would probably come
across, being on your back,

00:45:40.721 --> 00:45:42.220
and learning how
to fight, and being

00:45:42.220 --> 00:45:44.304
comfortable in those
scenarios is certainly great.

00:45:44.304 --> 00:45:45.928
But just the fact
that you can actually

00:45:45.928 --> 00:45:48.100
practice it without
getting injured, I think,

00:45:48.100 --> 00:45:49.700
is super important.

00:45:49.700 --> 00:45:51.980
