where you can't really

00:45:51.980 --> 00:45:55.426
afford to get scratched or
punched and have a black eye,

00:45:55.426 --> 00:45:56.047
it can happen.

00:45:56.047 --> 00:45:57.380
There's accidents in all sports.

00:45:57.380 --> 00:45:58.730
But I'd say jiu-jitsu.

