those de-escalation techniques.

00:47:43.020 --> 00:47:45.640
And they also have a
kids bully proof program.

00:47:45.640 --> 00:47:46.380
It's really cool.

00:47:46.380 --> 00:47:47.394
And it's all online.

00:47:47.394 --> 00:47:49.810
But they also have affiliate
schools all over the country.

00:47:49.810 --> 00:47:54.610
But I think what they're doing
is a subset of jiu-jitsu that

00:47:54.610 --> 00:47:57.850
really addresses the core
tenants of self-defense that's

00:47:57.850 --> 00:47:59.400
separate from the sport.

00:47:59.400 --> 00:48:01.379
So I definitely recommend that.

